105277.text: [105277] StaticText "From the globally bestselling author of the Chronicles of St Mary's series, a not-so-ladylike aristocrat meets the world's most unlikely butler, and together they bring a whole new meaning to partners-in-crime..."

105281.text: [105281] StaticText "'Clever, funny and made my heart hurt in the best way' "

105293.text: [105293] StaticText ", for whom there is no problem that can't be solved by a drink and a think."

105300.text: [105300] StaticText ', for whom there is no problem. Ever.'

105303.text: [105303] StaticText "Everyone's favourite time-travelling bounty hunters. Sorry - 'recovery agents'. No bad guy they can't handle. No expense account too flexible. No rule they cannot break."

105306.text: [105306] StaticText "As long as they're together, the world is their oyster. And they'll always have each other's backs, right?"

105310.text: [105310] StaticText "Fasten your seatbelts. The timeline doesn't know what's hit it."

105316.text: [105316] StaticText "Readers can't get enough of Smallhope and Pennyroyal..."

105320.text: [105320] StaticText "'I love this book! Love, love, love it' ⭐ ⭐⭐ ⭐⭐"

105323.text: [105323] StaticText "'Absolutely brilliant. Could not put it down. It literally ticks every box' ⭐ ⭐⭐ ⭐⭐"

105326.text: [105326] StaticText "'I laughed, I cried and sighed in pure contentment' ⭐ ⭐⭐ ⭐⭐"

105329.text: [105329] StaticText "'Funny and gut-wrenching at times... the ending had me on the edge of my seat' ⭐ ⭐⭐ ⭐⭐"

105332.text: [105332] StaticText "'Teasers that are just waiting to be unravelled, wicked villains, and an unexpected hookup' ⭐ ⭐⭐ ⭐⭐"

105335.text: [105335] StaticText "'A must read - especially if you want to learn to make a great margarita' ⭐ ⭐⭐ ⭐⭐"

105341.text: [105341] StaticText "'Jodi Taylor had given me so much joy, tears, drama and adventure in my life when I read her work that sometimes it's a disappointment to be in the real world' ⭐ ⭐⭐ ⭐⭐"
